nl_cmd: Pick up the pillow on the chair and put it on the grey sofa with a laptop in the living room. Place it next to the remote control.
Pick up the spray from the floor and place it on the bottom shelf of the TV stand next to the baseball bat.
Please bring the box from the TV room and drop it into the receptacle bin.
Please pick up the book from the wicker chair and place it on the chest of drawers.
Grab the apple off the chair next to the couch, then drop it in the box near the TV.
Take the apple and go into the corridor with the TV. Place it inside the pot that is next to the TV.
Grab the book from the orange couch and place it on the grey couch next to the laptop.
Go to the hallway and pick up the bottle and place it on the drawer next to the purple armchair.
Pick up the book on the brown bamboo chair and put the book on the TV stand, next to the pot.
Pick up the box in the living room next to the TV and put it on the bed in the bedroom.
Run to the bedroom and take the pillow on the bed in the bedroom and place it on the white sofa.
Go into the living room and grab the baskeball beside the couch. Then proceed to put it on the white chair.
Take the Sherlock Holmes book from the room with the round white table and place it on the bed in the bedroom.
Grab the mug next to the laptop and go to the living room and place it next to the TV.
Take the white book and drop it on the chair under the desert painting on the wall.
Pick up the book on the round white table and put it on the grey lounge chair.
Go to the office and pick up the spray and place it on the sofa in the living room.
Go pick up the fork and place it next to the laptop on my bed.
Run to the white drawer, grab the pen and bring it back to me in the bedroom.
Go to the living room, grab the newspaper off the grey couch, then place it on the yellow couch.
Go to the living room and grab the cell phone on the table, then come back to the bedroom and place it on the bed.
Move to the bedroom. Take the book from the bed and place it on the desk beside the bed.
Take the pencil from the grey sofa and place it on the round bedside table next to the bed.
Pick up the candle and place it by the apple on the table with the spray.
Go get the spray off the black dresser in the next room and trash it in my bedroom.
Pick up the glass from the lounge, take it to the bedroom and put it down on the chest of drawers.
Pick up the yellow vase on the brown table and then move to the lounge and place the book on the white table.
Go into the room with the television, pick up the remote, bring the remote into the room with the bed and place the remote on the bed.
Please pick up the alarm clock on the chest of drawers and take it and place it on the white sofa.
Go to the bedroom and pick up the basketball and place it on the sofa in the living room.
Go to the living room, grab the cup, then drop it in the recycling bin next to the laptop.
Get the vase from the table and put it on the sofa.
Take the remote control that is next to the TV and place it on the sofa.
Go to the end of the bedroom beside the cot. Pick up the basketball to the left of the baseball bat and place it by the TV.
Take the black mug from the white table with the laptop. Place the black mug on the coffee table next to the leafy plant.
Take the alarm clock from the table in the corridor and place it next to the plant on the table in the middle corridor.
Fetch the blue plate and put it on the shelf under the one with the pot.
Grab the spray from the coffee table with the plant. Place the spray on the black table next to the pepper.
Take the clock to the sofa chair.
Grab the pepper grinder from the table close to the TV and put it on the light brown dresser in the middle of the room.
Get the remote and place it in the can next to the television.
Find the blue plate on the stand and then go to the room with the television. Then find the bin and drop the plate inside.
